                    </did>
                    <scopecontent><p>A small collection of personal items including: certificates, awards, and medals presented to Serly; membership cards; the 1911 naturalization certificate of Lajos Serly and his family; postcards and items collected by Serly in Hungary; and official documents pertaining to Serly’s accidental death in London, including his death certificate.</p>
                    </scopecontent>
